quotes: I won't run away, I never go back on my word!
I'm going to become Hokage, believe it!
It's by failing that we become strong.
I will never let my friends down.
If you want to kill me, then hate me, detest me, and live with that hatred.
It's not the face that makes a man a monster, it's his choices.
I will never back down from a challenge.
Even if I have to suffer, I will keep moving forward.
